<eesti>Riigil&otilde;ivuseadust (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 10, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 ja 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 ja 349; 55, 365; 57, 372 ja 373; 59, 379; 60, &otilde;iend; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 ja 598; 95, 607 ja 611; 2001, 2, 2; 3, 4; 16, 69 ja 72; 27, 151; 31, 171; 34, 188 ja 189; 36, 201; 42, 235; 43, 238 ja 239) t&auml;iendatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>The State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 10, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 and 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 and 349; 55, 365; 57, 372 and 373; 59, 379; 60, correction notice; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 and 598; 95, 607 and 611; 2001, 2, 2; 3, 4; 16, 69 and 72; 27, 151; 31, 171; 34, 188 and 189; 36, 201; 42, 235; 43, 238 and 239) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 3 l&otilde;iget 2 t&auml;iendatakse punktiga 13 (2) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>1) clause 13 (2)) is added to subsection 3 (2) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"13 (2)) tervishoiuteenuste korraldamise seaduse alusel teostatavad toimingud"; </eesti>
<inglise>"13 (2)) acts performed pursuant to the Health Services Organisation Act;" </inglise>
<eesti>2) 7. peat&uuml;kki t&auml;iendatakse 6 (2). jaoga j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) Chapter 7 is amended by adding Division 6 (2) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"6 (2). jagu </eesti>
<inglise>"Division 6 (2) </inglise>
<eesti>Tervishoiuteenuste korraldamise seaduse alusel teostatavad toimingud </eesti>
